  (text "CONNECTIVITY NOTES:\\nAll Qwiic and Grove signals from STM32U585 (UNO Q MCU).\\nESP32-S3 does NOT drive these connectors.\\n\\nQWIIC (SparkFun/Adafruit spec: 3.3V I2C 100/400kHz):\\n  J8/J9 daisy-chain: electrically parallel\\n  4.7kΩ pullups R5/R6 on SDA/SCL to +3V3\\n  Cable: GND=black +3V3=red SDA=blue SCL=yellow\\n\\nGROVE connectors:\\n  J10 I2C:    SIG1=SDA SIG2=SCL (STM32U585)\\n  J11 UART:   SIG1=TX  SIG2=RX  (STM32U585)\\n  J12 SPI:    SIG1=MOSI SIG2=SCK (STM32U585)\\n  J13 Digital:SIG1=GPIO SIG2=GPIO\\n  J14 Analog: SIG1=ADC0 SIG2=ADC1\\n  All 3.3V max. Do not connect 5V Grove sensors."
    (at 30 100 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)) (justify left top))
    (uuid "b8939699-c92d-49bd-888f-a396f68a621c")
  )
